data.description: Highly sought out! Located in Beachwood Heights in Coral Springs. As you step inside this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage single family home, you're greeted by an inspiring living area leading to a gorgeous screened pool view! Also, pool views and access from the master bedroom and kitchen! Features High Vaulted Ceilings. New Laminate Scratch Resistant & Waterproof Floors throughout the house. The master suite is very spacious and has a walk-in closet. The open concept kitchen features wood cabinets and newer stainless-steel appliances. Outdoors, the screened pool area ensures a pleasant environment for entertaining guests surrounded by vegetation is very private. Conveniently located 15 minutes from I95 & just a 25-minute drive to the beach! This house is the perfect home! This one won't last!
